      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible, mint condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it just as much. It's a total dream to drive and looks absolutely stunning in person. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
