    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in pristine condition, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension setup utilizing aluminum control arms and gas-pressurized dampers that retain their original damping rates. Every mechanical tolerance meets factory specifications, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline remains as visceral as the day it left Regensburg.",
