    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in showroom condition as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are supple with no signs of wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous service history performed exclusively by authorized dealerships. It has been garage-kept under a soft cover in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing rain or snow. Every detail, from the spotless engine bay to the untouched factory floor mats, confirms its status as a top-tier example. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a documented maintenance log. This is an opportunity for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
