      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it's an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s truly in spotless, pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a charm and is totally ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
