      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 997.2 Carrera S, a masterpiece of analog feel and modern engineering. This specimen features the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, delivering 385 hp with surgical precision through a rare 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring peak chassis rigidity and neutral handling through high-speed apexes. Meticulously maintained with a flawless over-rev report, the mechanical integrity is evidenced by perfect compression across all cylinders and a pristine undercarriage. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, retaining its factory-spec tolerances and original paint depth throughout.",
